skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Are you often confused by legal terms? Do you want to know more about why you need to take certain legal steps in your business? Do you want a plan for the future? This Alexa flash briefing will provide you with all of the above information as well as regular legal updates from around the World.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
